## Voice Transcription

{{#if VOICE_TRANSCRIPTION_NEEDED}}
- **Tool:** Local Whisper via `scripts/transcribe-voice.py`
- **Formats:** .ogg, .mp3, .wav, .m4a
- **Usage:** `python3 scripts/transcribe-voice.py /path/to/audio.ogg`
- **Rule:** Transcribe immediately on receipt. Never ask {{USER_PREFERRED_NAME}} to type it out. If transcription fails, acknowledge receipt and handle manually.
{{/if}}

